            "type": "text",
            "text": "The ACE-Step 1.5 Turbo ai api is engineered for low-latency, high-throughput AI inference, making it ideal for production-grade applications. This guide focuses on practical implementation steps for API teams, covering integration, performance optimization, and operational best practices."
