            "type": "text",
            "text": "1. Integrating ACE-Step 1.5 Turbo AI API"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To integrate the ACE-Step 1.5 Turbo AI API, start by obtaining API keys from the provider dashboard. Use standard HTTP POST requests to the endpoint "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "https://api.acestep.ai/v1/turbo",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " with JSON payloads. Ensure your client handles authentication via Bearer tokens and supports streaming responses for real-time use cases. Example request:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code_block",
        "lang": "json",
        "value": "{\n  \"model\": \"ace-step-1.5-turbo\",\n  \"input\": \"Your prompt here\",\n  \"parameters\": {\n    \"max_tokens\": 150,\n    \"temperature\": 0.5\n  }\n}",
